+Install \fIFONTS\fR.  The default is to install the \fIunicode\fR font.
+
+.TP
+\fB--locales\fR=\fILOCALES\fR
+Install only locales listed in \fILOCALES\fR.  The default is to install all available locales.
+
+.TP
